Principle:
- simple (easy to use, less no of clicks, hides complexing with innovatiive uI)
- fast (fast respose , percived response)
- functional (all functions are working to the last detail)
- honest (no dirty hacks, cost, terms of use are transparent)


Features :
 - geolocation search by plz or street + house no (ongoing)
 - geolocation result ordered with distance info
 - save search filter
 - geolocation info is saved during advert save (preview step)
 - website redesign, common look and feel, buttons & logo design
 - price (basic and profi business pack)  last setup of wizard, billing address
 - upload file validation -check file size and max no. of images
 - gmap api key should be corretly setup
 - activating advert, advertisement management/placement - workflow ?
 - detail view has inserted date and last updated date
 - marker for newly inserted immobilien
 - validation for uploading data
 - api to integrate with immobilienscout24 and immowelt

